MercadoPago C# SDK
===================================

**.NET SDK for MercadoPago checkout and payments integration.**

By [Sergio Cirielli](https://github.com/volvin)

Description
-----------

This sdk allows you to create a checkout button and init a payment flow. Both modal and standard samples are included.

There is also a client to process income payment notifications.

Contributors
------------

* [Sebastián Gun](https://github.com/sebagun) - This Readme file

Third parties
-------------

* This software extends the Facebook library for the Graph API.
* And uses MercadoPago APIs (https://developers.mercadopago.com/).

